data.description: Welcome to The White House of Cordova. This beautiful home captivates the American Dream of the traditional home with a white picket fence! Inside, however, this beautifully custom designed 4 bedroom/4 Bath home opens to another realm of non-traditional elegance: Huge master bedroom and large additional bedrooms. Top of the line appliances, custom cabinets, huge pantry. Plantation shutters throughout, hardwood floors, Italian tile, brand new carpet, wonderful wraparound porch and patio.
